@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_amtxbn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v2 = (0.12 + 0.77)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v1 + 0.13 * tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = v1
    v1 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.58 + v0 + 0.99) / tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
